title: High Stepper
description: Step cake with shots fanning left to right and back again. Red & green pearls and crackling effects with loud reports. 220 shots in about 25 seconds! (Rapid Fire)

title: Fantastic
description: Fan shaped 500 gram repeater with; 1st Row: Aqua blue with lemon dahlia; 2nd Row: Brocade with red glitter; 3rd Row: Brocade with crackling flower; 4th Row: Aqua blue to red glitter; 5th Row: Aqua blue with lemon dahlia and red glitter; 6th Row: Red and green crackling willow.

title: Fireworks Factory
description: Starts with three 2" shots of red, white and blue peonies; Then sixteen shots of brocade to red; Red to crackling palm; Brocade to green; Green to crackling palm; Quickened final three 2" shots of brocade crowns.

title: Cascade
description: 500 gram repeater with awesome waterfall effects ending with extra large golden stars. Shoots four shots at a time.

title: Victory March
description: Red tail to blue peony with white glitter pistil; Silver tail to red peony with blue pistil; Blue tail to silver peony with red pistil; Red, white and blue peony with crackling pistil (Final three shots).
